{t:E-0005 (F) Bless the Lord, O my soul Magnify His wonderful name}
{st:}

E-0005 F Chord

Bless the Lord, O my soul,
Magnify His wonderful Name
For the glory of the Lord is mine
forever,
Jesus is ever the same;

For the Lord has set me free,
And He's given me liberty,
To tell the world that Jesus is mine,
He has given me the wine to make
my heart rejoice.
And oil to make my face to shine.


